<text><body>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"></cb:mulu><cb:div><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0001001" n="0001001"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0001a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連依教便<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="cb-app"/>脩<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>行</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">供養三尊及大眾</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">福利遐超<unclear></unclear>鬼趣</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">願我慈親領受之</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">因茲息苦得停酸</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">免受倒懸三<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>道</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">離却鬼前休<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>趣</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">得向<g ref="#CB29788">󷑜</g>園礼世尊</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">因此厥号<g ref="#CB07830">𥁄</g>蘭盆</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">接引眾生交離苦</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不獨當初為目連</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">兼為今朝座下人</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">故知大聖不思議</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">流向<g ref="#CB17591">𨶒</g>浮化羣生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">為救世間諸苦難</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">名曰<g ref="#CB07830">𥁄</g>蘭清淨經</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">念觀世音菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g><unclear></unclear></l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a10"/><p xml:id="pD03p0001a1001"><note place="inline">仏子</note>。將釋此經大分三叚苐一序分苐二正宗
<lb ed="D" n="0001a11"/>苐三流通分三叚不同且初序分。<note place="inline">仏子</note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a12"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0001a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">上来<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>即如斯</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">略与門徒分別<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">向下依經次苐陳</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不知道理復如何</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大眾<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="cb-app"/>須<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>生敬重心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><unclear></unclear>道此經<unclear></unclear>孝行</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">各各<g ref="#CB00866">𣫍</g>心合掌着</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">經文次苐唱將来</l></lg>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><p xml:id="pD03p0002a0101">經云聞如是一時。佛在舎衛國<g ref="#CB29788">󷑜</g>樹
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>給孤獨。</p><p xml:id="pD03p0002a0204" rend="inline"><note place="inline">仏子</note>。西方梵語名佛陁此
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/>土<g ref="#CB30244">󷘤</g>為求斍者。自斍〃他覺<anchor xml:id="beg_3" type="cb-app"/>行<anchor xml:id="end_3"/>圎滿。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0002a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">覺行周圎号世尊</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">於中三覺不思議</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">別日与門徒廣分別</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">今且略明<g ref="#CB11180">󲮬</g>妙法</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">願聞<unclear></unclear>障<unclear></unclear>消除</l></lg><p xml:id="pD03p0002a0608" rend="inline"><note place="inline">仏</note>言舎衛國<g ref="#CB29788">󷑜</g>樹給孤
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>獨園。<note place="inline">仏子</note>。舎衛國者好嘉名人物英雄心<anchor xml:id="beg_4" type="cb-app"/>猛<anchor xml:id="end_4"/>利。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0002a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">国王太子兼長者</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸佛如来<anchor xml:id="beg_5" type="cb-app"/>住<anchor xml:id="end_5"/>彼中</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">給孤長者湏達<anchor xml:id="beg_6" type="cb-app"/>多<anchor xml:id="end_6"/></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">聞佛功徳心中喜</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">火急<g ref="#CB08221">㱕</g>来造精舎</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">便買<g ref="#CB29788">󷑜</g>陁太子園</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">四十里地布黃金</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">建造如来說法<anchor xml:id="beg_7" type="cb-app"/>處<anchor xml:id="end_7"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">殿宇樓臺徦日月</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">池<g ref="#CB08887">󲊷</g>華菓用<g ref="#CB00982">㽵</g>嚴</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><unclear></unclear>仏當日在彼中</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>這<g ref="#CB07830">𥁄</g>蘭清淨教</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">為救目連慈母罪</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">免交受苦<unclear></unclear>生天</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">上来多叚義不同</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB30106">𢝰</g><g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>經文<anchor xml:id="beg_8" type="cb-app"/><space quantity="0"/><anchor xml:id="end_8"/>成就義</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a16"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">従此下反是別序</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連得道復如何</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a17"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大眾<unclear></unclear>生敬重心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">六通之名當解釋</l>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">各各虔茶合掌着</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連得道唱將来</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/><p xml:id="pD03p0003a0201">經云大目揵連始得六通。仏子。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0003a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">恰似世間慈母身</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">養得子時登官位</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">威勢人間皆<g ref="#CB30106">𢝰</g>怕</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">自出分憂佐大唐</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><anchor xml:id="beg_9" type="cb-app"/>忽<anchor xml:id="end_9"/>然憶着我耶孃</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">取向本州專侍奉</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">所得財物買珠瑱</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">將来奉獻我尊親</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">百味<g ref="#CB13251">󳏃</g>羞皆給恭</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">日夜將心親侍奉</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">若也悶来交合曲</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">音聲歌儛不曾<g ref="#CB09109">𠇲</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">朝〃甘脆父母前</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><anchor xml:id="beg_a" type="cb-app"/>晝<anchor xml:id="end_a"/>夜尋常居左右</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">所要之間皆<unclear></unclear>有</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">意徒孝行遣人傳</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">今此目連亦復然</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">得道恰似為官位</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">憶得先亡念慈親</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">堕落三塗阿郍邊</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">遂將天眼更遙觀</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">欲覓尊親擬供養</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">直為亡来年嵗久</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不知神識落何方</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><anchor xml:id="beg_b" type="cb-app"/>乃<anchor xml:id="end_b"/>知證得六神通</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">根本還因求父母</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a16"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">羅漢六通為苐一</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">願報當初養育<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a17"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">今此向下一唱經</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">欲度父母報<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>受</l>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大眾好生合掌着</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">經文次<anchor xml:id="beg_c" type="cb-app"/>第<anchor xml:id="end_c"/>唱將来</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a02"/><p xml:id="pD03p0004a0201">經云目連欲度父母報乳脯之<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>。仏子。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a03"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0004a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">自得既圎應合救物</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">懷其孝行欲報重<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a04"/><p xml:id="pD03p0004a0401">經云度者即是度脫報<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>兩字通摽經
<lb ed="D" n="0004a05"/>題。且夫人生在世。父母為親。非母不生。
<lb ed="D" n="0004a06"/>非母不長。是以目連。報其<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>徳。仏子。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a07"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0004a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連自得既周圎</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">理合救其親父母</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">心裏為懷行孝行</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">報<g ref="#CB31016">󷤨</g>従来養育<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">人生在世合如斯</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">父母深<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>湏報荅</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">想得當初養育我</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">受苦懷<unclear></unclear>不可論</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">除其孝順在眼前</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">供給<anchor xml:id="beg_d" type="cb-app"/><space quantity="0"/><anchor xml:id="end_d"/>所湏不闕少</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">假使砕身千万刼</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不能報得母深<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">將知<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>徳大難酬</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">我佛如来再三<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">奉勸座下佛弟子</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">大湏孝順莫因循</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a15"/><p xml:id="pD03p0004a1501">仏子。故父母<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>重經云。父母有十種<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>卆
<lb ed="D" n="0004a16"/>難報荅。</p><list><item xml:id="itemD03p0004a1604">一者懷胎守護<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0004a1611">二者臨產
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0005a" n="0005a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a01"/>受苦<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0104">三者生子妄憂<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0111">四者<g ref="#CB09727">𠰸</g>苦
<lb ed="D" n="0005a02"/>吐甘<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0204">五者迴乾就濕<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0211">六者乳
<lb ed="D" n="0005a03"/>脯養育<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0305">七者洗濯不淨<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0312">八者為
<lb ed="D" n="0005a04"/>造<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>業<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0405">九者遠行憶念<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0412">十者究
<lb ed="D" n="0005a05"/>竟憐愍<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></item></list><p xml:id="pD03p0005a0505" rend="inline">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0005a0507" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">適来雖<anchor xml:id="beg_e" type="cb-app"/>列<anchor xml:id="end_e"/>十<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>名</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">義理差殊都未解</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">門徒若要細分別</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">先生敬重後依行</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">苐一懷擔守護<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">十月胎中常負重</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">慈母將心憂姟子</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB06960">𢙢</g>怕胎中不得安</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">生時受苦命如斯</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">赤血滂沲魂魄散</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">時向之間<g ref="#CB30220">󷘌</g>却命</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">由怕姟兒有<g ref="#CB02167">󰡷</g>殤</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">生了心中便喜歡</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">忘却憂愁如快樂</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">眷属親情皆<g ref="#CB30106">𢝰</g>喜</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">慶賀今朝母子安</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">漸〃姟兒長大時</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">乾處唯留與子眠</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">濕處迴將母自臥</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">洗濯之時無懈惓</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">乳脯養育不辝勞</l>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0006a" n="0006a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">寒熱都来為<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">怜念由如掌上珠</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a02"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">年登十五母由憂</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB06960">𢙢</g>怕造諸不善業</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">走去心中常憶念</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">仏前發願早<g ref="#CB08221">㱕</g>来</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">四時八莭不前頭</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不覺<anchor xml:id="beg_f" type="cb-app"/>目<anchor xml:id="end_f"/>中雙淚下</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">時向之間不得見</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">恛惶惆悵似湯<g ref="#CB10781">𤋎</g></l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a06"/><p xml:id="pD03p0006a0601">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0006a0603" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">他家孝順由憂耶孃</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不孝之男廣造<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>業</note></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">他州外鄉逐樂不<g ref="#CB08221">㱕</g></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">父母此間肝膓寸断</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a08"/><p xml:id="pD03p0006a0801">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0006a0803" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">他家若是孝順之兒</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">解向家中親侍奉</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">若是心中不孝順</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">逃走他鄉<g ref="#CB30106">𢝰</g>不<anchor xml:id="beg_10" type="cb-app"/><g ref="#CB08221">㱕</g><anchor xml:id="end_10"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">囙脩向外嵗年間</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">逐樂何曾憶父母</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">所得錢財別受用</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">肯解將来獻二親</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">將知世界<g ref="#CB01618">𨒫</g>眾生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">罪過愚膚不可<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">不報其<g ref="#CB22131">㤙</g>不孝順</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">堕向三塗<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>道中</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">奉勸門徒諸信心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">莫作如斯不孝人</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">斈取目連心裏<unclear></unclear></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">命終必<g ref="#CB30070">㝎</g>見慈尊</l></lg>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0007a" n="0007a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0007a01"/><p xml:id="pD03p0007a0101">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0007a0103" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">上来道理轉殷勤</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">聞道還湏行
<lb ed="D" n="0007a02"/>孝行</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不但自家心裏了</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">也令眾罪
<lb ed="D" n="0007a03"/>速消除</l></lg><p xml:id="pD03p0007a0304" rend="inline"><g ref="#CB07830">𥁄</g>蘭盆經<g ref="#CB09083">󲍻</g>
<lb ed="D" n="0007a04"/>觀。故題。此經讚<unclear></unclear>不思冝留傳天下
<lb ed="D" n="0007a05"/>眾人知有緣得遇<anchor xml:id="beg_11" type="cb-app"/>者<anchor xml:id="end_11"/>蓮花<anchor xml:id="beg_12" type="cb-app"/>會裏<anchor xml:id="end_12"/>与君<g ref="#CB21991">𠋣</g>。</p></cb:div>
</body>
